
camera_node       - RPi software to do camera and image works...
camera_test_app   - PC (and/or Mac) based software to connect to camera node, used for test and development
dimmer_node       - optional arduino/teensy software for mains dimming...
light_control_app - PC (and/or Mac) based app to control the main node, used for test, development and maintenance
light_node        - arduino/teensy software for light control node
light_test_app    - PC (and/or Mac) based application to test light_node software
main_mode         - RPi software to collect activity data from cams, control scenarios and orchestrate the lights
